Class ResampleImage_

  • java.lang.Object
    • ResampleImage_
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ij.plugin.filter.PlugInFilter

    public class ResampleImage_
extends java.lang.Object
implements ij.plugin.filter.PlugInFilter
    ImageJ plugin to resample an image to a lower number of counts. Assumes that the pixel values in the image correspond to the number of photons detected at that pixel.

    David Platten, 2019
